---
title:  Rigatoni and Double Chorizo Rosé Marinara with Roasted Pepper Pesto and Spinach
description: This creamy rosé sauce is a game changer for weeknights. Our easy cheat version uses cream cheese to add richness without making the dish too heavy. Plus, the delicious turkey flavour shines through!
